<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sifaks Ousmail | Official Website</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Official website of Sifaks Ousmail. Coming soon." />

  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #111827, #1e1b4b);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .container { max-width: 720px; }

    .tag {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #c4b5fd;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(42px, 8vw, 86px);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 span { color: #a78bfa; }

    p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .link:hover {
      background: rgba(167,139,250,0.2);
      border-color: #a78bfa;
    }

    footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="container">
    <div class="tag">Official Website</div>

    <h1>SIFAKS OUSMAIL<br><span>COMING SOON</span></h1>

    <p>
      Personal website for research, projects, and academic work.
    </p>

    <a class="link" href="mailto:coachmedanny@gmail.com">Contact</a>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Sifaks Ousmail
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
